Package: sceptre
Type: Package
Title: Conditional resampling differential expression analyses for pooled CRISPR screens
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gene Katsevich, Tim Barry, Kathryn Roeder
Maintainer: Tim Barry <tbarry2@andrew.cmu.edu>
Description: This package contains functions for performing differential expression analyses in single-cell pooled CRISPR screens based on conditional resampling.
